  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of study is to test whether perioperative sodium bicarbonate infusion can prevent
      acute kidney injury following open heart surgery in infective endocarditis patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
